                <li><a href="about.html">Nagu Saabsan</a></li>
                <li><a href="contact.html">Nala Soco</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Ku Soo Dhowow Supermarket-ka Badbaado</h1>
        <p>Halkan waxaad ka helaysaa alaab kasta oo qoyskaagu u baahan yahay oo tayo leh.</p>
        <a href="products.html" class="btn">Eeg Alaabta Aan Ibinayno</a>
    </section>

    <section class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Maxay Macaamiishu Noogu Dooranayaan?</h2>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
                <h3>Qiimo Jaban</h3>
                <p>Waxaan kuu haynaa qiimo ku habboon jeebkaada iyo dalabyo joogto ah.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <h3>Alaab Tayo Leh</h3>
                <p>Dhammaan khudaarta iyo hilibka aan iibinno waa kuwo cusub maalin kasta.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col">
                <h3>Adeeg Degdeg ah</h3>
                <p>Shaqaalaheenu waxay had iyo jeer u taagan yihiin inay kuu adeegaan si dhakhso leh.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Badbaado Supermarket. Xuquuqda way dhowran tahay.</p>
    </footer>

